    <li>Deployed a fully functional AI meeting minute tool built by i.AI</li>
    <li>Uploaded a meeting recording and had it transcribed by AWS Transcribe</li>
    <li>Generated structured meeting minutes using Amazon Nova Pro via Amazon Bedrock</li>
    <li>Used AI-powered editing to refine the output</li>
    <li>Explored multiple meeting templates</li>
    <li>Exported minutes as a Word document</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
    <strong>The time savings are significant.</strong> What traditionally takes 2 to 4 hours
